<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Grade 8 Science - Sound Interactive</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #2c3e50;
            --accent: #9b59b6;
            --success: #27ae60;
            --danger: #e74c3c;
            --bg: #fdfefe;
        }

        * { box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, sans-serif; }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            background: #eef2f3;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Branding Layer */
        #brand-layer {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background: white;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            z-index: 2000;
        }
        #brand-layer img { max-width: 200px; height: auto; }

        /* Animation Background */
        .wave-bg {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            z-index: -1;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dae2f8 0%, #d6a4e4 100%);
        }

        .sound-wave {
            position: absolute;
            border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: pulse 4s infinite linear;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { width: 0; height: 0; opacity: 1; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); }
            100% { width: 500px; height: 500px; opacity: 0; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); }
        }

        /* Main Container */
        .game-card {
            width: 95%;
            max-width: 700px;
            background: white;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        .hidden { display: none !important; }

        /* Progress & Timer */
        .hud {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .timer-track {
            width: 100%;
            height: 6px;
            background: #eee;
            border-radius: 3px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        #timer-bar {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: var(--accent);
            border-radius: 3px;
            transition: width 1s linear;
        }

        /* Question Layout */
        h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 15px; }

        .img-container {
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .img-container img {
            max-height: 180px;
            max-width: 100%;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        .options-grid { display: grid; gap: 10px; }

        .opt-btn {
            background: #fff;
            border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
            padding: 12px 15px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: left;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: 0.2s;
        }

        .opt-btn:hover:not(:disabled) { border-color: var(--accent); background: #fdf7ff; }

        .correct { background: var(--success) !important; color: white; border-color: #219150; }
        .wrong { background: var(--danger) !important; color: white; border-color: #c0392b; }

        .feedback-box {
            margin-top: 15px;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            background: #f9f9f9;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
        }

        .btn-next {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            float: right;
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* Result */
        .result-title { font-size: 2rem; color: var(--accent); margin: 10px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div id="brand-layer">
        <img src="assets/logo.png" alt="Innovine Logo">
    </div>

    <div class="wave-bg" id="waves"></div>

    <div class="game-card">
        <div id="screen-start">
            <h1>Chapter 4: Sound</h1>
            <p>Grade 8 Science | Competency-Based Challenge</p>
            <p>Test your knowledge on frequency, vibrations, and how sound travels!</p>
            <button class="btn-next" style="float:none" onclick
